  "title": "Supplier Quality Engineer (Manufacturing, East)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities: </strong></p><ul><li>Manage supplier quality and act as primary quality contact for suppliers.</li><li>Oversee material specifications, supplier QA agreements (QAA), SQC, and early alert systems; coordinate sign-offs with suppliers.</li><li>Ensure only materials meeting specifications are released to production.</li><li>Collaborate with FMOS and Global/Local Procurement & Logistics teams to manage approved suppliers consistently.</li><li>Establish, maintain, and report supplier quality KPIs regularly.</li><li>Conduct periodic supplier and on-site contractor performance reviews.</li><li>Align and standardize supplier quality and incoming QC processes across the company.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Engineering or equivalent. </li><li>Minimum 3 years’ experience in audits and management systems.</li><li>Strong knowledge of Quality Management Systems and auditing.</li><li>Familiar with statistical techniques and quality tools (FMEA, MSA, SPC).</li></ul><p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p><p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p><p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p><p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p><p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p><p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p><p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p><p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p><p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p><p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
